Description:
    Install Miti Rails integration

    This generator adds the necessary configuration to use Miti's Nepali
    calendar helpers, form helpers, date picker, and model concern in
    your Rails application.

    It will:
      1. Pin the Stimulus date picker controller in config/importmap.rb
      2. Register the Stimulus controller in app/javascript/controllers/index.js
      3. Add the Miti stylesheet to your application CSS
      4. Add the calendar data script tag to your application layout

Example:
    bin/rails generate miti:install
